About Taj Lake Palace Udaipur

The Hotel Taj Lake Palace Udaipur is a luxurious haven of bliss and a 5-star experience. Located at a wonderful location with a great atmosphere, it offers a perfect blend of classic old-time charm and modern elegance. The hotel's well-designed and maintained rooms are comfortably furnished and come with stunning views. The staff provides exceptional service, making guests feel like royalty. The culinary experiences at the hotel's restaurants are outstanding, with a diverse range of delectable dishes from around the world. The hotel also offers a range of amenities including a fitness centre, spa and wellness centre, outdoor pool, and free WiFi. It is the perfect choice for vacations, weddings, and parties.

Mythic hotel that should consider a serious lifting to be a true international 5* hotel
Exceptional to take a little boat to reach the hotel on the Lake Pichola, a myth!! Beautiful architecture from inside, a place with charm and a lot of character, Very good food at the continental restaurant and good breakfast. Nice local show for guests at 5.45pm + nice excursions organised to other island. Nice little pool and nice Hamman
The hotel is shabby in places - for a 5* hotel this should be corrected. The gym is a joke and not to standards one could expect from an international chain such a TAJ. It would also be nice to tip at the end of the stay (like it is done in other 5* hotels) instead of tipping each time and everyday. A bit of a pain....Breaksfast is very nice but not enough space around the buffet + staff overwhelmed by number of people (we had to wait to get bowls to serve ourselves fruits, wait for milk, ... on both mornings - we stayed 2 nights). Very expensive compared to other 5* as well... The most expensive of all our 3 weeks stay in India... Is it really worth it?
